items.sentence: Tom has done everything Mary asked him to do.
Tom has decided to give Mary a second chance.
Tom has already told Mary what she should do.
Tom has a pen, but he doesn't have any paper.
Tom explained his plan to both Mary and John.
Tom doesn't want to give his old car to Mary.
Tom doesn't want to be a computer programmer.
Tom doesn't think Mary really had to do that.
Tom doesn't plan on staying here much longer.
Tom doesn't know why the picnic was canceled.
